%N A014879 Inverse of 870th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A014879 Periodic with period length 870. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 06 2017
%H A014879 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A014879/b014879.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..1000</a>
%H A014879 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 870.
%H A014879 <a href="/index/Rec#order_224">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 224.
%H A014879 <a href="/index/Pol#poly_cyclo_inv">Index to sequences related to inverse of cyclotomic polynomials</a>
%p A014879 with(numtheory,cyclotomic); c := n->series(1/cyclotomic(n,x),x,80);
